Each quark mass may be evaluated at its self-scale or at any SM particle mass within its perturbative running window. Top does not run (decays before hadronizing). Round-number scales are excluded. Light quarks have no perturbative self-scale. The complete scale list is archived as \texttt{search\_space.json}~\citep{RepoMC}.

Trial count (audited; complete enumeration in \texttt{trial\_list\_complete.csv}):
\begin{equation}
20\;\text{triples} \times 4\;\text{signs} \times (\text{variable scales}) = 12{,}960\;\text{trials exactly.}
\end{equation}


